name: *Luxury Penthouse in the heart of trendy Zurich*
description: Modern and unique penthouse apartment over three stories. Located in the heart of Zürich West: with art, design, food, culture, shopping & architecture in the center of attention. Spacious,  luxury apartment with large Terrace, whirlpool, bbq, fireplace, gourmet kitchen and much more. Perfect access to public and private transport. Currently renovating main kitchen hence certain limitations (dishwasher & oven are to be found on the rooftop 2nd Kitchen)
neighborhood_overview:
Zurich is hip-circuit with the Swiss peacefulness!

Zurich-West – From Industrial Quarter to Trendy District
The district in the west of Zurich is full of contrasts, boasting an unpolished charm. Where ships were once built and engines bolted together, art, design, food, culture shopping and architecture are now the center of attention. Factories have moved away, leaving their vast expanses of space that creative minds have taken advantage of. The coolest place to live, work, dine, go clubbing in Zurich. This was a former industrial areas that has developed in a hybrid living working cultural space

description:
MONTHLY RENTAL ONLY

This luxurious 3-bedroom apartment is located in the heart of Zurich in one of the best neighbourhoods in town.

It is ideal for expats looking to spend over a month in the city for business or pleasure.

Several supermarkets, bank, pharmacy, post office, other shops and restaurants are all in walking distance. The lake and city center are only a short stroll away.

host_about: I am Delphine from Switzerland and I manage a portfolio of serveral properties in Isla Holbox, Mexico and Zurich, Switzerland.   As hospitality school graduate and passionate traveller, I have travelled around the world for all my life and hence know the importance of excellent customer service. After my hospitality management studies in Switzerland I moved to Mexico to open a backpacker hostel and to manage several luxury properties on Isla Holbox. Recently I have acquired addtional properties to rent in my hometown Zurich and I now divide my time between the two countries. I am always available for my guests on my Mexican whatsapp number listed here or whenever possible personally on-site to help with any questions or to organize any additional services that might be desired. I pride myself to have high quality standards and to know the distinct needs of the budget to luxury traveller. Don't hesitate to contact me for any inquiries.

name: Cozy studio in the city center
description: This summer I sublet my super cozy studio apartment in the middle of Kreis 4, the hip area of Zurich! There are plenty of bars and cafés right in the neighborhood and a cute park is only two minutes walk away. The area is very lively especially at weekends but the apartment is very quiet if you close the windows. The main train station and all the great places of Zurich like the lake or the old town are in walkable distance and if you feel less energetic there are plenty of trams and buses.
